<bibRefCitation author="Moure" box="[749,928,1187,1214]" firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="97 - 160" refId="ref21372" refString="Moure J. S. 1960. Notes on the types of the Neotropical bees described by Fabricius (Hymenoptera: Apoidea). Studia Entomologica 3 (1 - 4): 97 - 160." type="journal article" year="1960">Moure (1960)</bibRefCitation>
